  --------------- --------------- ----------------------------------------------
  n8n             Qdrant          http://qdrant:6333

  n8n             Ollama          http://ollama:11434

  n8n             PostgreSQL      postgresql://user:pass@postgres:5432/corpfit

  n8n             Claude API      https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages

  Browser         n8n             http://localhost:5678

  Browser         Qdrant          http://localhost:6333/dashboard
